data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Wedgefield golf community, where luxury and leisure meet! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, built in 2021, is a masterpiece of modern living. Boasting a prime location with a front yard view of the 18th hole, this property offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and scenic beauty.    The entire house is adorned with wood like tile flooring, offering both durability and aesthetic appeal. The heart of this home is the kitchen, where sleek quartz countertops and LG stainless steel appliances come together to create a chef's paradise. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or simply love gathering with family and friends, this kitchen is sure to impress.    The master suite is a spacious sanctuary, providing a peaceful retreat after a long day. It features a generously sized closet, perfect for organizing your wardrobe and accessories. The master bathroom is a true oasis, with high-end finishes and plenty of natural light.    One of the highlights of this property is the covered and screened back patio, where you can enjoy the Florida sunshine all year round. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue, this outdoor space is the perfect place to make memories with loved ones.    Practicality meets convenience with overhead storage racks in the garage, ensuring that all your storage needs are met without compromising the cleanliness and organization of the space.    Wedgefield golf community is known for its beautiful surroundings, outstanding amenities, and a sense of community that is second to none. This home provides an opportunity to experience the best of Florida living while being part of a close-knit neighborhood.    Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a home that combines luxury, functionality, and a prime location. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this magnificent property your own. Your new life of comfort, style, and relaxation awaits in Wedgefield!
